reviewText: My daughter loves this movie so much I had to get one. I couldn't find white chicks nowhere till I checked here. Thanks for saving me.
Package came damaged. The case is cracked and missing a piece.

bought used, item described as smudges on case, case was devastated with scratches that were very visible. But at the end of the day its the DVD that really matters. The DVD arrived like brand new with 0 scratches and played perfectly. Despite scratches on case i did buy it used and happy with purchase
